  "prompt": "What are some of the funniest YouTube videos?",
  "response": "YouTube is a treasure trove of hilarious content, and humor is subjective, but here are some timeless funny videos that have entertained millions:\n\n### Classic Funny Videos:\n1. **\"Charlie Bit My Finger\"**  \n   A classic viral moment of two British brothers where one playfully gets bitten by the other.\n\n2. **\"David After Dentist\"**  \n   A young boy\u2019s post-dental anesthesia ramblings that became an internet sensation.\n\n3. **\"Double Rainbow\"** (YosemiteBear)  \n   A man\u2019s emotional and over-the-top reaction to seeing a double rainbow in Yosemite.\n\n4. **\"Sh**t Girls Say\"** (by Graydon Sheppard and Kyle Humphrey)  \n   A hilarious parody of stereotypical things women say.\n\n5. **\"Ultimate Dog Tease\"**  \n   A dog owner narrates what his dog is thinking as he\u2019s teased with food.\n\n### Comedy Channels & Skits:\n6. **Key & Peele**  \n   Their skits, like the \"Substitute Teacher\" or \"East/West Bowl,\" are comedy gold.\n\n7. **The Lonely Island**  \n   Known for their music parodies like \"I\u2019m on a Boat\" and \"J*** in My Pants.\"\n\n8. **SNL Digital Shorts**  \n   Memorable hits like \"D*** in a Box\" and \"Lazy Sunday.\"\n\n9. **CollegeHumor**  \n   Hilarious sketches like \"If Google Was a Guy\" or \"The Job Interview.\"\n\n10. **Mr. Bean**  \n   Official clips of Mr. Bean\u2019s silent physical comedy are always a hit.\n\n### Funny Animations & Shorts:\n11. **\"The Duck Song\"** (by Bryant Oden)  \n   A catchy, funny song about a duck asking for grapes.\n\n12. **\"Simon\u2019s Cat\"**  \n   Adorable and funny animations about a mischievous cat.\n\n13. **\"The Badger Song\"** (by Weebl)  \n   A quirky and absurdly catchy tune about a badger.\n\n### Pranks & Challenges:\n14. **\"JK News\" Pranks**  \n   Over-the-top pranks by JK News that often leave people in stitches.\n\n15. **\"Try Not to Laugh Challenges\"**  \n   Compilations of funny clips that test your ability to keep a straight face.\n\n### Memes & Random Humor:\n16. **\"Hide the Pain Harold\" Compilations**  \n   The iconic stock photo guy turned into endless memes.\n\n17. **\"Distracted Boyfriend\" Meme Videos**  \n   Creative takes on the infamous stock photo.\n\n18. **\"Salt Bae Memes\"**  \n   Videos and compilations inspired by the viral Salt Bae chef.\n\n### Animal Antics:\n19. **\"Surprised Kitty\"** (Talking Cat)  \n   A cat\u2019s adorable reaction to being woken up.\n\n20. **\"Dramatic Chipmunk\"**  \n   A short video of a chipmunk with a hilarious zoom-in effect.\n\nThese are just a few examples, but YouTube\u2019s algorithm is great at recommending more based on your sense of humor!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
